Speaking Engagements


Financial Innovation and Payments Summit2017 Opal Group / Newport, RI






12.15.2016




            COALA African Blockchain Workshop: Blockchain for Identity & Privacy



    

Speaking Engagements


    PanelistCOALA African Blockchain Workshop / Nairobi, Kenya


                
Blockchain technologies offer new opportunities for secure and non-counterfeitable identity platforms and systems. Yet, the decentralized nature of these technologies raises important concerns when it comes to establishing the identities of users.

            



